                "actions": {
                    "value": 3
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The shocker lizard hunkers down and begins to spark with electricity, which it releases in a 10-foot emanation that deals [[/r 3d8 #electricity]]{3d8 electricity damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"18\" data-pf2-traits=\"electricity,evocation,primal,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Shocking Burst DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>\n<p>The shocker lizard can't use Shocking Burst again for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>Up to four shocker lizards can combine their Shocking Bursts. In this case, the lizards can delay the release of their electricity until any other shocker lizard within 30 feet completes its Shocking Burst. The combined Shocking Bursts create an emanation with the combined area from all participating shocker lizards. For each additional shocker lizard that joins the burst, the damage increases by 3d8 and the save DC increases by 1 (to a maximum of four lizards dealing 12d8 damage with a DC 21 save).</p>"
